Security & Ritual Invariants (Quick Read)

One active Visa per World ID (world_nullifier) across the entire ecosystem; issuance reverts if an active Visa exists.

Soulbound: Visa NFT is non-transferable; burn on revocation.

Revocation thresholds: configurable MAX_STRIKES (default 3) + instant revocation for severe reasons (fraud, sybil orchestration, oracle tamper).

Propagation: Emitted RevocationBroadcast must be consumed by partner registries; @requires(trusted_emitters).

Privacy: Store commitments only (nullifier/root/merkle) — never PII.

Sabbath: All mutating functions are guarded by respect_sabbath() unless emergency_pause=true signed by Crown/Council.

Appeals: Oracular Council multi-sig (3-of-5 Elders) decides Reinstate | Uphold.

World ID: Require zk proof verification bound to holder address as signal.


